window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Death waits in the shadows, stalking my every move. </b></p> <p>Family is everything. So when my sister ran away to be with her new boyfriend, I chased after her.</p> <p>A strange, crimson-eyed man attacked me within minutes of my arrival, only to bring me my destiny.</p> <p>Alex, an arrogant, handsome flirt, saved me. No matter how hard we try to fight our connection, we're drawn to each other.</p> <p>While he reluctantly agrees to help me, I discover a terrifying new world filled with creatures that shouldn't be real; shifters, vampires, angels, witches, and so much more.</p> <p>Every minute I'm in Shadow Terrace becomes increasingly more dangerous, but Iâ€™ll risk everything to save my sister.</p> <p>Even if it means turning my back on the man who could possibly complete my soul.</p> <p><b>If you can't get enough of books by Patricia Briggs, Ilona Andrews, Linsey Hall, Leia Stone, and Jaymin Eve, then you'll love this paranormal romance.</b></p> <p><b>Scroll up and buy </b><b><i>Cursed Mate</i></b><b> today.</b></p>"; 
